{
  "texts": [
    "Therefore, the full potential of integrated convolutional neural network (CNN) models, DWT feature extraction, and support vector machine (SVM) classification may enhance the detection and segmentation of colorectal cancer.",
    "After completing the preprocessing, we stored the images from the CKHK-22 dataset in Google Cloud.",
    "To facilitate the training and testing of the proposed PolynetDWTCADx system, this procedure facilitates the rapid access and modification of the dataset.",
    "We designed the system to identify and delineate colorectal cancer using Google Colab Pro+, Keras, and TensorFlow libraries.",
    "To ensure adequate assessment of the model, we divide the pre-processed CKHK-22 dataset into training and testing sets."
  ]
}